@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_cguvxc(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.cos((tmp + 0.16 * v1 + 0.70)))
    v2 = wp.cos(0.41)
    v1 = v2
    tmp = wp.sin(tmp)
    v1 = wp.sin((0.78 - 0.38))
    tmp = v1
    tmp = ((0.92 / (v2 + 0.17 + v2 + 0.36)) + ((tmp + 0.71 + v0 + 0.14) * wp.abs(tmp + 0.94)))
    v0 = (tmp * 0.82)
    data[tid] = v0
